GetStreamIdConvention

Gets or sets the stream id convention. The default searches for [OutputStreamAttribute], if not present will return name of class and make it friendly (Generic names will be nicely formated). Used in:

  • Rehydrate
  • Read
  • SaveChanges
  • SaveNew
SteamNameConvention GetStreamIdConvention { get; set; }

Property Value

SteamNameConvention

The get stream identifier convention.

GetStreamIdSnapshotConvention

Gets or sets the stream identifier snapshot convention. The default appends "Snapshot" suffix to the name found in [OutputStreamAttribute], if not present then will append to the name of class. Used in:

  • GetSnapshot
  • AppendSnapshot
SteamNameConvention GetStreamIdSnapshotConvention { get; set; }

Property Value

SteamNameConvention

The get stream identifier snapshot convention.

StreamNameFromEventConvention

Gets or sets the stream name from event convention. This is used only in AppendEvent. The default searches for [OutputStreamAttribute]. If not found than the last segment of the namespace is used as category, that is not named "Events".
